description: Citation network for snowballing. 'refs' = papers each paper references (backward snowball: who do they cite?). 'cited_by' = papers that cite each paper (forward snowball: who cites them?). Only internal edges (both papers in platform). Short work IDs (W-prefix). For external snowballing, query OpenAlex directly: https://api.openalex.org/works?filter=cites:<work_id>
